Package com.ibm.di.connector.tam

Provides classes for the TAM connector.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommonBase
    Utility class to enable classes to log to the LogProxyImpl
    Domain  
    Group
    Group class contains the functionality to find, add, modify and delete Groups from TAM using the TAM Connector for IBM Tivoli Directory Integrator.
    Policy  
    SSOCredentials
    SSOCredentials class contains the functionality to find, add, modify and delete SSO Resource Info from TAM using the TAM Connector for TDI.
    SSOResource
    SSO Resource class contains the functionality to find, add and delete Resources from TAM using the TAM Connector for IBM Tivoli Directory Integrator.
    SSOResourceGroup
    SSO Resource Groups class contains the functionality to find, add, modify and delete Resource Groups from TAM using the TAM Connector for IBM Tivoli Directory Integrator.
    TAMConnector
    The TAM Connector.
    TMSMessageGetter
    Wrapper class used to retrieve TMS messages for the TAM Connector.
    TMSMsgId
    Typesafe enum of the TAM Connector message ids
    User
    User class contains the functionality to find, add, modify and delete Users from TAM using the TAM Connector for IBM Tivoli Directory Integrator
